data.description:
PENTHOUSE PERFECTION!

The Grandview Suite P-302, 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath + Separate Office Space

Enjoy the panoramic Southeastern views (Downtown, Midtown, and Buckhead skylines) from this beautifully appointed Penthouse level two bedroom plus den home in Buckhead’s Grandview Condominium. There are grey contemporary engineered hardwoods throughout the residence. Just off the entry hallway is the open living and dining space with a wall of windows (with custom roller shades) viewing downtown. The focal point of the living room space is a contemporary custom built in entertainment center. A galley kitchen with breakfast bar overlooks the dining area. The kitchen features a premium stainless steel appliance suite, undermount farm sink, white Quartz counters and immaculate white cabinetry.

The second bedroom is off the living room and has a generously sized walk-in closet. The Spa like bathroom has floor to ceiling marble tile and a glass enclosed tub/shower with jetted tub and steamer. Glassed French doors from the living room lead into the Owners retreat space with a den/office space (with custom built-ins). The main bedroom has access to a large wrap-around balcony space which doubles as extra entertaining space (wall mounted exterior flat panel television). The main bathroom has solid wood grey cabinetry, double vanities, marble counters and floors and a frameless glass shower stall with inset stone floors.

The amenities at The Grandview include a 24-hour Concierge, pool, sauna, two gyms, theatre and club house. The Lenox MARTA Station, Lenox Mall, Phipps Plaza and multiple restaurant and entertainment venues are all with easy walking distance. Two premium assigned covered parking spaces + storage space are included with the sale of the home.
